{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They get the-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At Christmas, they get off a few week, I think, a few days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's some kind of a summer vacation, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, of course, we didn't have to go to school then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was-- we looked forward to that, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't have to go on the [INAUDIBLE], you know, and we were out there somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we were looking for that, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was about two or three weeks, I think, we had off, you know what I mean, from the school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I want you to know something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had that wagon, like I showed you in one of the pictures, one of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember, that wagon was 6 to 7 feet long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was almost like a circus wagon, if you really look at it, but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was special-- my dad had a wagon made every year, every year, new wagon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because being the-- [GERMAN], the business handler the way he was, and the end of the season, in August, end of August-- they called it Arolsen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a big-- like a fair there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the Gypsies, all the [GERMAN] men that came there with their animals, with the-- this and the cows and the horses and the sheep, and-- that's where all the business was done.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arolsen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a town, Arolsen, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's very known for that-- like Pomona here, for the fair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This Arolsen was known for this, to-- to those [GERMAN] with the animal kingdom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, they had rides, and this and that, and music, and [INAUDIBLE], whatever they had there, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was every year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my dad pulled up-- they were all waiting already.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
